  <section class="text-center pt-16 pb-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 mx-auto leading-tight">
      Boston Women in
      <span class="text-accent dark:text-white highlight">Bioinformatics</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Team up with <span class="font-semibold">US</span>, your pathway to elevating your career through leadership,
      networking, and professional growth.
    </p>
